nhc_headline: ...BARBARA HAS BECOME A REMNANT LOW... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY...
summary: ...BARBARA HAS BECOME A REMNANT LOW... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY... As of 8:00 PM MST Tue Jun 10 the center of Barbara was located near 21.2, -108.0 with movement N at 5 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1007 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 30 mph.
